		<div id="comment_body_64882305"><p>I bought HiperCalc Pro and it keeps getting significant new features.  My kids use it too for their advanced math classes and prefer it to a TI.</p><p>A good blend of traditional calculator and phone capabilities.</p><p>cz.hipercalc.pro on Android - maybe iPhone people can get it too.</p><p>It's just nice to see small developers still making great software.</p></div>
